Dialogue: 0,00:00:18.33,00:00:09.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,00:00:23.00,00:00:09.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,作事
Dialogue: 0,00:00:45.66,00:00:47.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Royalkguard! No one moves\n皇家卫兵搜查谁都不准动
Dialogue: 0,00:00:52.00,00:00:54.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,think that's a safe bet\n我想那样应该万无一失
Dialogue: 0,00:00:55.66,00:00:57.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,The outlaw, Princess Djana\n有人看见逃犯裘娜公主
Dialogue: 0,00:00:57.66,00:01:00.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,and her friends have been\nseen in the neighbourhood\n她的朋友在这附近露面
Dialogue: 0,00:01:00.66,00:01:03.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You haven't seen them\nhave you, innkeeper\n你没有见到她们吗店老板
Dialogue: 0,00:01:04.00,00:01:06.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,mean no offence, your Lordship\n我无意冒犯您殿下
Dialogue: 0,00:01:06.33,00:01:07.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,but with all\nthe taxes these days\n可从这几天的酒菜钱来看
Dialogue: 0,00:01:08.00,00:01:10.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I get very few customers\n我这都没几个顾客光临啊
Dialogue: 0,00:01:10.33,00:01:15.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You are aware of what happens\nto anyone who harbours rebels?\n你会留意有谁包庇那些逃犯的吧
Dialogue: 0,00:01:15.33,00:01:18.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes my Lord, I value my-life\n噢当然殿下我很珍惜自己生命的
Dialogue: 0,00:01:22.00,00:01:23.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,We've searched\neverywhere, Lord bragado\n我们到处都搜遍了布拉刚
Dialogue: 0,00:01:24.00,00:01:25.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,There's no"trace of them\n没有他的踪影
Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.66,00:01:25.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,515
Dialogue: 0,00:01:32.33,00:01:33.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You're not having anything?\n你们不喝点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,00:01:34.00,00:01:36.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Not even a little herbal tea?\n要不要来点清凉茶啊
Dialogue: 0,00:01:41.33,00:01:42.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Flaming dragons\n燃烧的龙啊
Dialogue: 0,00:01:43.00,00:01:45.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,When nt comes\nto harbouring\nrebe\n提到匿藏逃犯
Dialogue: 0,00:01:45.33,00:01:47.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,no one can hold\na candle to silkarl\n没大比塞尔未更擅长了
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.66,00:01:47.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.00,00:01:52.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks, Silkar\n没错谢谢塞尔卡
Dialogue: 0,00:01:52.66,00:01:53.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You were perfect\n你刚才表现真不错
Dialogue: 0,00:01:53.66,00:01:56.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,though your chimney\ncould use a good cleaning\n不过你的烟囱需要好好清洗一番了
Dialogue: 0,00:01:56.33,00:01:58.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I'mfamishe\nWhat'slon the menu?\n我饿了今天准备了什么吃的啊
Dialogue: 0,00:01:59.66,00:02:02.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,What aboutHerik'?▲\nIsn't he eating with you?\n哈里克呢他不跟你们一起吃吗
Dialogue: 0,00:02:02.33,00:02:04.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,His eminence is meditating\n他出众的地方航是沉思
Dialogue: 0,00:02:04.33,00:02:06.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Worldly things\njust don' t interest him\n尘世的东栖他都没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,00:02:06.33,00:02:08.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Not even my Fangor stew\n他对我的炖梵高都没兴趣吗
Dialogue: 0,00:02:09.00,00:02:10.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Go and/ fetch him will you Wip?\n威普你去把他找来行吗
Dialogue: 0,00:02:11.00,00:02:14.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I knew it!I knew\nit was too good to last.\n我就知道好事持续不了多长时间
Dialogue: 0,00:02:22.00,00:02:24.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Herik! Herik! Wake up!\n哈里克哈里克醒醒
Dialogue: 0,00:02:25.00,00:02:26.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Theyre waiting\nfor us at the inn!\n她们在酒馆等我们呢
Dialogue: 0,00:02:27.00,00:02:27.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,威普你平吗要打断我
Dialogue: 0,00:02:28.00,00:02:31.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,was just about to pass\nthrough the portal of telepathy!\n刚要通过传心木之门啊
Dialogue: 0,00:02:31.66,00:02:31.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,On司同mpy8ma动h\n你要饿册等御吗
Dialogue: 0,00:02:32.00,00:02:33.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,On aneetmply stomache\n你要饿\n行吗
Dialogue: 0,00:02:33.33,00:02:35.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Come on\nlet's go have some lunch\n来吧我们去吃午餐
Dialogue: 0,00:02:36.00,00:02:39.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,1. won't need lunch, Wip\non the other side of the portal\n还在传心术门外我不需要吃午餐威普
Dialogue: 0,00:02:49.66,00:02:39.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,t
Dialogue: 0,00:02:55.00,00:02:57.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Well, my lovelies\n我的宝贝们
Dialogue: 0,00:02:57.33,00:03:00.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,what is it that you have\nspoted that I should know about?\n你们给我带回什么好消息了啊
Dialogue: 0,00:03:03.00,00:03:06.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Aahh… the young Shogi.\n啊是那个小术士
Dialogue: 0,00:03:07.33,00:03:09.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I won't need anything\n我不需要吃什么东西
Dialogue: 0,00:03:10.33,00:03:13.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,My spirit will/ be\nfree from physical limits\n我的灵魂会摆脱肉体的控制
Dialogue: 0,00:03:13.66,00:03:16.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I'll travel great, distar\nn the blink of angele\n后一眨眼间穿越长远距离
Dialogue: 0,00:03:17.00,00:03:20.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,But Herik\nDo it after lunch\n哈里克用完午餐再说行不行叫
Dialogue: 0,00:03:20.66,00:03:23.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Sillar has prepared\na real feast and\n塞尔卡准备一顿丰盛的天餐
Dialogue: 0,00:03:23.66,00:03:26.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Oh no, her's-gone again!\n哦不他又离开
Dialogue: 0,00:03:27.33,00:03:26.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,罗
Dialogue: 0,00:03:38.66,00:03:42.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Morgan. Morgan?\n莫刚莫刚
Dialogue: 0,00:03:42.66,00:03:47.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Morgan? Do you hear me?\nAnswer! It's me, Herik.\n莫刚听到我说话吗请回答\n是我哈里克
Dialogue: 0,00:03:54.00,00:03:55.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,What's this\n这是什么把戏
Dialogue: 0,00:03:55.33,00:03:59.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,It seems the young Shogi,\nhas found the telepathic portal!\n看样子小术士找到了传心术之门
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.66,00:04:02.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Very dangerous, little Shogi\n真危险啊小术士
Dialogue: 0,00:04:02.33,00:04:07.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,t leaves them both exposed\n就这样把你的肉体和灵魂暴露在
Dialogue: 0,00:04:07.66,00:04:10.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,to those with more\nskill in such matters!\n你更擅长传心术的人面前
Dialogue: 0,00:04:11.66,00:04:14.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Come, my Griffins\n过来我的兽兵
Dialogue: 0,00:04:37.66,00:04:14.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,L
Dialogue: 0,00:04:38.00,00:04:40.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Herik? Hey, ane you alright?\n哈里克嘿你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,00:04:41.00,00:04:42.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Please say something\n说话啊
Dialogue: 0,00:04:43.33,00:04:46.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Come on,\\nSilkar's stew is getting cold\n点塞尔卡准备的美味要凉了
Dialogue: 0,00:04:47.00,00:04:46.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,吗
Dialogue: 0,00:05:08.66,00:04:46.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,会
Dialogue: 0,00:05:16.66,00:04:46.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,V
Dialogue: 0,00:05:18.00,00:05:21.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Now, you shall obey me\n现在开始你要服从我的命令
Dialogue: 0,00:05:26.33,00:05:29.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Herik? We're\nhonoured by your presence\n哈里克你来了我们真感到荣幸
Dialogue: 0,00:05:30.33,00:05:33.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Wait for your chance,\nthen take Xcalibur\n等待机会拿到神剑
Dialogue: 0,00:05:34.00,00:05:37.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,and bring it to me\nalong with the Book of Life\n然后把它和生命之书一起带来给我
Dialogue: 0,00:05:38.33,00:05:37.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,s
Dialogue: 0,00:05:39.66,00:05:42.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Taste this. Choice Fangor\n尝尝这个我的炖梵高
Dialogue: 0,00:05:44.00,00:05:45.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Lost your appetite\n没胃口吗
Dialogue: 0,00:05:51.66,00:05:52.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,guess not.\n看来不是
Dialogue: 0,00:05:55.00,00:05:56.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Herik\n哈里克
Dialogue: 0,00:05:57.00,00:05:56.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,00:06:08.33,00:06:11.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! A Griffin!\n有怪兽
Dialogue: 0,00:06:11.66,00:06:14.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Help! mama\n救命妈妈
Dialogue: 0,00:06:14.66,00:06:15.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,O
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.66,00:06:18.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Mama! MaMa\n妈妈妈妈
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.33,00:06:20.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Back, beast! Get away!\n滚回去怪兽滚
Dialogue: 0,00:06:24.66,00:06:26.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Griffins are more\nferocious than that\n怪兽向来不是很凶残的吗
Dialogue: 0,00:06:27.00,00:06:28.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,/He must be il\n他肯定是有点不正常
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.66,00:06:28.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,auo amll Au
Dialogue: 0,00:06:29.00,00:06:30.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,It's all right\nlittle- one\n没事了我的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,00:06:30.33,00:06:31.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Mama is here\n妈妈在这
Dialogue: 0,00:06:36.00,00:06:39.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I guess you'll be returning to\nyou precious studies, eh, Herik?\n我想你要回去继续钻研吧哈里克
Dialogue: 0,00:06:43.00,00:06:45.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,How about a good siesta first!\n先好好午休一下如何啊
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.00,00:06:47.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You should at\nleast get\ngood rest\n在你继续传心术修炼之前
Dialogue: 0,00:06:48.00,00:06:50.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,before you go through that\nportal where you don't eat\n你至少得好好休息下吧\n到那时候连吃的都没有
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.00,00:06:52.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere Herik\n哈里克要去哪
Dialogue: 0,00:06:55.66,00:06:57.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Better get cleaned up first\n不过你最好先整理下自己
Dialogue: 0,00:06:57.66,00:07:00.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You dont want to\nmake a bad first impression\n你也不想留个不好的第一印象吧
Dialogue: 0,00:07:00.33,00:07:02.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Now! Take the sword\n趁现在把神剑拿到手
Dialogue: 0,00:07:05.66,00:07:07.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Herik! No!\n恰里克不要
Dialogue: 0,00:07:07.66,00:07:07.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,N\n哈里克不要
Dialogue: 0,00:07:12.00,00:07:14.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,No! You-might hurt Herik\n习能会伤到哈里克
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.66,00:07:26.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Hey! Give that back!\n嘿把生命之书还来
Dialogue: 0,00:07:27.33,00:07:29.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,He cant go fa\n他走不了多的
Dialogue: 0,00:07:32.66,00:07:34.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Take care of Herik\n照顾一下哈里克
Dialogue: 0,00:07:42.00,00:07:44.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Not quite yourself\ntoday, are you, Herik?\n哈里克今天真不象你是不
Dialogue: 0,00:07:55.00,00:07:57.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,What do you want\nthat Book for. Griffin?\n怪兽你拿生命之书做付啊
Dialogue: 0,00:07:57.66,00:07:59.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,You lcan't even read!\n你害还都看不
Dialogue: 0,00:08:02.66,00:08:04.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,What happened, Herik?\n哈里克发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,00:08:04.33,00:08:05.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,It's,not like you\n这可一点不象你
Dialogue: 0,00:08:05.66,00:08:07.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,to let one of these\nprimitive beasts beat you\n被这个原始动物打倒子啊
Dialogue: 0,00:08:08.00,00:08:09.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,I'll get him!\n我会抓到他的
Dialogue: 0,00:08:09.33,00:08:09.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,我会抓到他的
Dialogue: 0,00:08:24.66,00:08:27.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,-Quiet, you miserable donkey\n占你
Dialogue: 0,00:08:27.66,00:08:27.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,T
Dialogue: 0,00:08:33.33,00:08:34.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,We have them, my lord\n我们找到他了殿下
Dialogue: 0,00:08:34.33,00:08:36.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,The young Shogi\nand the Barbarian!\n是小术士和蛮族人
Dialogue: 0,00:08:36.66,00:08:38.33,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,What about Djana?\n还有裘娜呢
Dialogue: 0,00:08:38.66,00:08:41.00,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,don't know. I see only two\n我不清楚只找到两个
Dialogue: 0,00:08:41.33,00:08:42.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,Don' t lose sight of them?\n别跟丢他们了
Dialogue: 0,00:08:43.00,00:08:42.66,神秘岛,,0,0,0,,They'l. lead\nus to the princess\n他会带我们找费的
